Install dependencies for compiling / running the app
----------------------------------------------------
Python dependencies can be installed via PIP:
- sudo easy_install pip
- sudo pip install -r requirements.txt

Additional software on the developer machine:
- Oracle Java 7 JDK
- ANT
- Beanstalkd 

Additional software on the production machine:
- Oracle Java 7 JRE
- PostgreSQL database
- Beanstalkd

Compile install packages to ./dist on developer machine
-------------------------------------------------------
./setup.py build
./setup.py sdist

Install new release on production machine
------------------------------------------
tar xvfz FuzzEdx.xx.tgz .
./manage.py syncdb
./manage.py migrate

